data.description: WELCOME HOME! This beautiful property is sure to steal your heart. Situated in a prime location just off IH 10, this home offers convenience and comfort.As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the modern upgrades and attention to detail. The kitchen boasts new stainless steel appliances, complemented by elegant granite countertops. With two separate dining areas and a breakfast nook, there's plenty of space for entertaining guests or enjoying family meals. Natural light pours in through new dual-pane windows, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere throughout the home. Step outside to the back patio and envision evenings spent relaxing or hosting barbecues in the spacious outdoor area. A convenient breezeway leads to the converted garage, providing a perfect she/he shed or a guest house. Situated on a huge corner double lot spanning over 1/4 acre, this property offers ample outdoor space for gardening, recreation, or expansion possibilities. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a move-in ready home with modern amenities and timeless charm. Schedule a showing for this one ASAP.
